/*賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭
# Root
賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭*/
@import url("../../../css/root.css");
/*賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭
# Todays Best Deals
賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭*/
.TodaysBestDeals {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  padding-top: var(--main-padding-top);
  padding-bottom: var(--main-padding-bottom);
}
.TodaysBestDeals .container {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 30px;
}
.TodaysBestDeals h1 {
  font-family: "Darumadrop One", cursive;
  font-weight: 700;
}
.TodaysBestDeals .container .nav-menu {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  height: fit-content;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  display: flex;
  gap: 10px;
}
.TodaysBestDeals .container .nav-menu li span {
  position: relative;
  padding: 8px 15px;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  border-radius: calc(var(--main-border-radius) * 5);
  border: 0.5px solid var(--white-alt-2);
  transition: var(--main-transition);
  color: #000;
  cursor: pointer;
}
.TodaysBestDeals .container .nav-menu li span.active {
  background-color: #003d29;
  color: var(--white-color);
  border: 0.5px solid #003d29;
}
/*賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭
# Todays Best Deals cards-container
賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭*/
.TodaysBestDeals .container .cards-container {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(250px, 1fr));
  gap: 15px;
}
/*賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭
# Todays Best Deals cards-container card
賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭*/
.TodaysBestDeals .container .cards-container .card {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  cursor: pointer;
}
.TodaysBestDeals .container .cards-container .card .header {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  border-radius: var(--main-border-radius);
  overflow: hidden;
  background-color: var(--white-alt-1);
}
.TodaysBestDeals .container .cards-container .card .header img {
  position: relative;
  width: 250px;
  height: 250px;
  transition: var(--main-transition);
}
.TodaysBestDeals .container .cards-container .card:hover img {
  transform: scale(1.3);
}
.TodaysBestDeals .container .cards-container .card .header i {
  position: absolute;
  top: 15px;
  right: 15px;
  font-size: 18px;
  cursor: pointer;
  background-color: #fff;
  padding: 15px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  transition: var(--main-transition);
}
.TodaysBestDeals .container .cards-container .card .header i:hover {
  background-color: #ff000082;
  color: #fff;
}
.TodaysBestDeals .container .cards-container .card .footer {
  position: relative;
  padding: 10px 0;
}
.TodaysBestDeals .container .cards-container .card .footer .info {
  position: relative;
  background-color: transparent;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
}
.TodaysBestDeals .container .cards-container .card .footer .info span {
  position: relative;
  font-size: 18px;
  font-weight: bold;
}
.TodaysBestDeals .container .cards-container .card .footer .info span.Price {
  position: relative;
  padding: 0 25px 0 15px;
  font-weight: bold;
  width: fit-content;
}
.TodaysBestDeals
  .container
  .cards-container
  .card
  .footer
  .info
  span.Price::before {
  content: " .00";
  position: absolute;
  top: -1px;
  right: 5px;
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: normal;
}
.TodaysBestDeals
  .container
  .cards-container
  .card
  .footer
  .info
  span.Price::after {
  position: absolute;
  content: "";
  font-family: "Font Awesome 5 Free";
  font-weight: 900;
  content: "\24";
  top: -1px;
  left: 0px;
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: normal;
}
.TodaysBestDeals .container .cards-container .card .footer p {
  position: relative;
  font-size: 14px;
  margin: 10px 0;
}
.TodaysBestDeals .container .cards-container .card .footer .stars {
  position: relative;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: flex-start;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 2px;
  margin: 10px 0;
}
.TodaysBestDeals .container .cards-container .card .footer .stars i {
  color: #47c20a;
}
.TodaysBestDeals .container .cards-container .card .footer button {
  position: relative;
  border-radius: calc(var(--main-border-radius) * 5);
  padding: 8px 15px;
  border: 0.5px solid #888;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: var(--main-transition);
  background-color: transparent;
}
.TodaysBestDeals .container .cards-container .card .footer button:hover {
  background-color: #47c20a;
  border: 0.5px solid #47c20a;
  color: #fff;
}
