/*賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭
# Root
賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭*/
@import url("../../../css/root.css");
/*賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭
# Popular Products
賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭*/
.PopularProducts {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  padding-top: var(--main-padding-top);
  padding-bottom: var(--main-padding-bottom);
}
.PopularProducts h1 {
  font-family: "Darumadrop One", cursive;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 30px;
}
.PopularProducts .card {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  cursor: crosshair;
}
.PopularProducts .card .header {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  border-radius: var(--main-border-radius);
  overflow: hidden;
  background-color: var(--white-alt-1);
}
.PopularProducts .card .header img {
  position: relative;
  width: 250px;
  height: 250px;
  transition: var(--main-transition);
}
.PopularProducts .card:hover img {
  transform: scale(1.3);
}
.PopularProducts .card .header i {
  position: absolute;
  top: 15px;
  right: 15px;
  font-size: 18px;
  cursor: pointer;
  background-color: #fff;
  padding: 15px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  transition: var(--main-transition);
}
.PopularProducts .card .header i:hover {
  background-color: #ff000082;
  color: #fff;
}
.PopularProducts .card .footer {
  position: relative;
  padding: 10px 0;
}
.PopularProducts .card .footer .info {
  position: relative;
  background-color: transparent;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
}
.PopularProducts .card .footer .info span {
  position: relative;
  font-size: 18px;
  font-weight: bold;
}
.PopularProducts .card .footer .info span.Price {
  position: relative;
  padding: 0 25px 0 15px;
  font-weight: bold;
  width: fit-content;
}
.PopularProducts .card .footer .info span.Price::before {
  content: " .00";
  position: absolute;
  top: -1px;
  right: 5px;
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: normal;
}
.PopularProducts .card .footer .info span.Price::after {
  position: absolute;
  content: "";
  font-family: "Font Awesome 5 Free";
  font-weight: 900;
  content: "\24";
  top: -1px;
  left: 0px;
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: normal;
}
.PopularProducts .card .footer p {
  position: relative;
  font-size: 14px;
  margin: 10px 0;
}
.PopularProducts .card .footer .stars {
  position: relative;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: flex-start;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 2px;
  margin: 10px 0;
}
.PopularProducts .card .footer .stars i {
  color: #47c20a;
}
.PopularProducts .card .footer button {
  position: relative;
  border-radius: calc(var(--main-border-radius) * 5);
  padding: 8px 15px;
  border: 0.5px solid #888;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: var(--main-transition);
  background-color: transparent;
}
.PopularProducts .card .footer button:hover {
  background-color: #47c20a;
  border: 0.5px solid #47c20a;
  color: #fff;
}
.PopularProducts .progress {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  height: 10px;
  background-color: var(--white-alt-1);
  border-radius: var(--main-border-radius);
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: var(--main-transition);
  margin: 10px 0;
}
.PopularProducts .progress .propress-per {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  transition: var(--main-transition);
  background-color: var(--blue-color);
  height: 100%;
}
