/*賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭
# Root
賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭*/
@import url("../../../css/root.css");
/*賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭
# Top Categories
賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭賭*/
.TopCategories {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  padding-top: var(--main-padding-top);
  padding-bottom: var(--main-padding-bottom);
}
.TopCategories .container h1 {
  font-family: "Darumadrop One", cursive;
  font-weight: 700;
}
.TopCategories .container .cards-container {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(165px, 1fr));
  gap: 20px;
  margin-top: 30px;
}
@media (max-width: 776px) {
  .TopCategories .container .cards-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(150px, 0.5fr));
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 30px;
  }
}
.TopCategories .container .cards-container .card {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  height: 300px;
  background-color: transparent;
  border-radius: var(--main-border-radius);
  overflow: hidden;
  cursor: pointer;
}
.TopCategories .container .cards-container .card img {
  position: absolute;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  object-fit: cover;
  transition: var(--main-transition);
}
.TopCategories .container .cards-container .card h5 {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 5;
  color: #fff;
  font-size: 25px;
  padding: 10px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  text-align: center;
  font-family: "Darumadrop One", cursive;
  font-weight: 700;
}

.TopCategories .container .cards-container .card:hover img {
  transform: scale(1.3);
}
